<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(169,169,169,0.6) 0%, rgba(169,169,169,0.6) 50%), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1426927308491-6380b6a9936f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1502&q=80');">
  <div class="banner-content">
    <h1>Borrowbox</h1>
    <p>Stop buying. Start borrowing.</p>
    <div class="searchbar">
      <%= form_tag items_path, method: :get do %>
      <%= text_field_tag :name,
      params[:name],
      class: "form-control",
      placeholder: "Find an item"
      %>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to items_path, class: "btn btn-primary" do %>
        <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h2> A credit based system cultivating a fair and balanced community, enabling people to lend and borrow lesser-used items.</h2>
    </div>
     <div class="row row-cards">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Minimalistic </br> & </br>Economical</h3>
         <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"></i>
          <p>Why store something you hardly use? Sharing leads to less consumerism helping the environment and your wallet as you stop spending money on rarely used items.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Community Oriented </br> & Convenient</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          <p>Shops all closed? That's ok, borrow it! On your way meet your neighbours through lending and borrowing!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Safe</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
          <p>Ratings and reviews builds trust.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

